  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scaling up UNIDO#s flagship #Bridge for Cities# initiative</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x201C;Bridge for Cities&#x201D; has become UNIDO&#x2019;s flagship initiative related to urban-industrial development. However, the &#x201C;Bridge for Cities&#x201D; initiative has so far been conducted as a series of stand-alone events, loosely connected and with little concrete follow-up in between. Also, insufficient linkages with UNIDO&#x2019;s technical cooperation programmes related to urban-industrial development were established.

The project will address these issues by institutionalizing and internationalizing the initiative, by continuously leveraging partnerships, resources and investments among the participating cities and by establishing clear linkages to UNIDO&#x2019;s technical cooperation programmes, including sustainable cities initiatives under PCPs. Moreover, in order to make &#x201C;Bridge for Cities&#x201D; more developmental, attention will be devoted to attract and involve cities from developing countries, including those participating in the Belt and Road Initiative.</narrative>
  </description>
